```plantuml
@startuml i5ting_stuq-koa
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor Developer

rectangle "Koa.js Application" as KoaApp {
  rectangle "Middleware" as Middleware #lightgrey
  rectangle "Routes" as Routes #lightyellow
  rectangle "Controllers" as Controllers #lightblue
  rectangle "Models" as Models #lightgreen
}

rectangle "MongoDB" as Database #mistyrose

rectangle "External Services" as ExternalServices #aliceblue

rectangle "Test Suite (Ava)" as TestSuite #lightpink

' ========== Connections ==========
Developer --> KoaApp : Develop/Run/Test

' Koa.js Application interactions
KoaApp --> Middleware : Use middleware for\nrequest/response processing
Middleware --> Routes : Pass control to routes

Routes --> Controllers : Forward requests
Controllers --> Models : Interact with data

Models <--> Database : CRUD operations

Controllers <--> ExternalServices : Integrate external APIs/services

' Testing
TestSuite --> KoaApp : Execute tests

@enduml
```